    "page": "magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006_6",
    "text": "The IONIQ 5 is proven worldwide for its prowess in electrification and sustainability. With its global award-winning DNA, Hyundai now begins a pivotal journey with the",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.059160316250337006,
      0.8139534884090307,
      0.6183206109634032,
      0.8415697673177137
    ],
    "page": "magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006_7",
    "text": "IONIQ 5 robotaxi, a level 4 autonomous vehicle that can drive without a driver. More than 30 sensors including LiDAR, and a computing system allows the robotaxi to detect 360° and make optimal decisions. Hyundai is beginning production of the",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.057251906722665453,
      0.8459302332052104,
      0.6183205983822966,
      0.889632936298413
    ],
    "page": "magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_magazine_TheEconomist.2023.11.25_page_006_8",
    "text": "IONIQ 5 robotaxi, which is set to launch in Las Vegas during the first half of 2024.",
